ingredientsDesc:
1. Tracer: Iodine-125 labelled anti-thyrotropin antibody (monoclonal, mouse), red colored. 21 ml each vial (< 600 kBq), 1 vial (or 2 vials).
2. Coated Tubes: coated with anti-thyrotropin-antibody (monoclonal, mouse), per box 50 tubes, 2 x 50 (or 4 x 50) tubes.
3. Washing solution: concentrate (50x), 11 ml each vial. 2 vials (or 3 vials).
4. TSH Standards: human serum. 7 vials. 0.5 ml each vial.
5. TSH Control sera K1, K2, and K3: human serum. 3 vials 0.5 ml each vial.
